data.description: Incredible open concept home in the highly desireable Masonboro Loop Rd. area! Situated on a spacious corner lot, this home boasts a design that was well before its time. Over $70,000 in tasteful updates in the past year which include, custom gourmet kitchen with beautiful quartz countertops, contemporary state of the art appliances with glass facades, Bathroom updates, expanded storage, New hardware and light fixtures, fresh paint, all new LVP flooring throughout home, new gutters, updated irrrigation system, and more!! Less than one mile from Masonboro Yacht Club and the New Hanover County Municipal Boat Ramp. This is Coastal living at its finest!!!!
